abstract: Emphasizing the country’s need for experienced leadership, Oliver Davis, a longtime council member in the city, has been a frequent critic of Mr. Buttigieg.
snippet: Emphasizing the country’s need for experienced leadership, Oliver Davis, a longtime council member in the city, has been a frequent critic of Mr. Buttigieg.
lead_paragraph: SOUTH BEND, Ind. — An African-American official of South Bend, Ind., endorsed Joseph R. Biden Jr. for president on Friday, snubbing the city’s mayor, Pete Buttigieg, in a close-to-home example of Mr. Buttigieg’s struggle to attract black support.

abstract: Michael R. Bloomberg, the former mayor of New York City and expected presidential candidate, is buying ads in more than two dozen states.
snippet: Michael R. Bloomberg, the former mayor of New York City and expected presidential candidate, is buying ads in more than two dozen states.
lead_paragraph: Michael R. Bloomberg, the billionaire former mayor of New York City, spent at least $30 million on Friday for a single week of television ads, a show of financial force that signals his willingness to use his vast personal fortune to reshape the Democratic presidential race.

headline_main: Bloomberg Prepares Huge TV Blitz, Reserving $30 Million in Ads
headline_print_headline: Bloomberg Will Flood Airwaves  In a $30 Million Week of TV Ads

abstract: For years, artists have put pressure on Facebook and Instagram to treat female and male nipples equally, but such a change may be too radical for Silicon Valley.
snippet: For years, artists have put pressure on Facebook and Instagram to treat female and male nipples equally, but such a change may be too radical for Silicon Valley.
lead_paragraph: Photographers have learned to be inventive in evading Instagram’s ban on female nipples. They’ve used paint, glitter, hair and flower petals to obscure them. They’ve covered them up with leaves, cornstarch, a spatula, handbags, shot glasses, strands of bubble gum, and sand.

abstract: They wanted to take down Biden. But they also wanted to absolve Moscow of election meddling.
snippet: They wanted to take down Biden. But they also wanted to absolve Moscow of election meddling.
lead_paragraph: The Ukraine scandal now unfolding in congressional impeachment hearings has at its core a Shakespearean twist: President Trump, abetted by his paladins of spin, has trapped himself in an alternate universe. To undermine the well-established fact that Russia corrupted the 2016 vote to help him win, Mr. Trump and his allies have tried to build a fiction that pins those crimes on Ukraine.

abstract: Lise Davidsen, a 32-year-old soprano starring in “The Queen of Spades,” has swiftly risen to the top of the field.
snippet: Lise Davidsen, a 32-year-old soprano starring in “The Queen of Spades,” has swiftly risen to the top of the field.
lead_paragraph: When you hear about the soprano Lise Davidsen, you might find yourself questioning the facts. Could someone who didn’t even see an opera until she was in her 20s really be making her Metropolitan Opera debut at 32? Surely she hasn’t been singing opera for only a decade?

abstract: Chop wood, carry water and other lessons that apply far beyond the gym.
snippet: Chop wood, carry water and other lessons that apply far beyond the gym.
lead_paragraph: One of my favorite movements at the gym is called a farmer’s carry. You hold a heavy weight — for me, around 95 pounds — in each hand and attempt to walk with a solid, upright posture for between 30 and 60 seconds.

abstract: The musician, who’s releasing his 14th album, “Hyperspace,” shares the 500-year-old paintings, Italian films and New York bookstore that top his list of essentials.
snippet: The musician, who’s releasing his 14th album, “Hyperspace,” shares the 500-year-old paintings, Italian films and New York bookstore that top his list of essentials.
lead_paragraph: “I’m drawn to things that feel like they were made at the wrong time,” said the stylistically restless musician Beck, recalling a formative trip to Madrid’s Prado museum while on tour early in his career. It was his first encounter with Hieronymus Bosch — who painted like a contemporary of Salvador Dalí even though he began work on his wild masterpiece “The Garden of Earthly Delights” way back in 1490. (“I’ve always intended to try and write an album based on that painting,” Beck, 49, said. “I’m not sure how that would work.”)

abstract: For several months, our writer searched for information about the Moranbong wristwatch. It wasn’t as simple as it sounds.
snippet: For several months, our writer searched for information about the Moranbong wristwatch. It wasn’t as simple as it sounds.
lead_paragraph: TOKYO — At first sight, the wristwatch looks rather ordinary: a minimalist white dial with a date window, silver hands and hour markers, on a simple silver-colored metal bracelet.

abstract: For 40 years, journalists chronicled the eccentric royal family of Oudh, deposed aristocrats who lived in a ruined palace in the Indian capital. It was a tragic, astonishing story. But was it true?

lead_paragraph: NEW DELHI — On a spring afternoon in 2016, when I was working in India, I received a telephone message from a recluse who lived in a forest in the middle of Delhi.
